      • add

        public Vector add(Vector _vector)
        Description copied from interface: Vector
        Adds the given vector to this vector, element by element, returning the sum in a new vector. The vector implementation class of the result is the same as that of this instance. Throws an IllegalArgumentException if the given vector is missing or is a different length than this instance.
        Specified by:
        add in interface Vector
        Parameters:
        _vector - the vector to add to this vector.
        Returns:
        a new vector containing the element-by-element sum of this instance and the given vector.
